    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！\nレッスン見に来てくれたの？",
      "startTime": 4.1000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど打ち合わせが終わったからな\n調子はどうだ？",
      "startTime": 9.0650093158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "無理はしないようにしたし\nすっごくいい調子だよ！",
      "startTime": 12.3000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスコーチも芽衣のことを褒めていたぞ",
      "startTime": 14.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　なんて言ってたの？",
      "startTime": 17.099999078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "以前とは見違えるぐらい\n動きが良くなってきているそうだ",
      "startTime": 21.2666659672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "元々ダンスが得意で飲み込みも早い方だったが\n最近は特に成長しているように感じると言っていたぞ",
      "startTime": 27.1666659672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "やった～！　教えてもらったことを\nちゃんと寮でも復習するようにしてるんだ～",
      "startTime": 34.2666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、夜更かしはしないように気を付けてるよ",
      "startTime": 37.7666651089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今まで通り努力して、工夫して、しっかり前進していく\nこの前言っていた目標の通りだな",
      "startTime": 47.1000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、この前は\nマネージャーストップをかけられちゃったからね",
      "startTime": 52.2000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーを心配させるアイドルじゃ\nファンのみんなも心配させちゃうでしょ？",
      "startTime": 58.3544037819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "後、今度の番組でどんなことを話すか、なんだけど\nあんまり長いと聞いてて分かんなくなっちゃいそうだし",
      "startTime": 66.833331871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "「デビューした時と同じ気持ちでアイドルを\n一生懸命頑張ります」って一言だけ言おうかなって！",
      "startTime": 73.3000015895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣らしい言葉でいいと思うぞ\nそれに……あいつも、麻奈も、そう言いそうだ",
      "startTime": 81.5000015895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どんなに有名になっても変わらず……\n「ただ、目の前の人達のために歌うだけだよ」って",
      "startTime": 89.847270286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん！　麻奈ちゃんならそう言いそう\nなんだかますます番組が楽しみになってきちゃったよ～",
      "startTime": 98.2666646957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "これまで楽しいことばっかりじゃなかったけど\n芽衣は、ファンのみんながいたから頑張れた",
      "startTime": 105.3999944687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなだけじゃなくて\nいろんな人が芽衣のことを応援してくれた",
      "startTime": 111.4333400089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣から元気をもらったって言ってくれて嬉しかった\nだから、その気持ちをみんなに伝えられたらいいな",
      "startTime": 118.8666657129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "startTime": 124.1333279607,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9903362000027,
          "startTime": 125.3333182969
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2666516302
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2666516302
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.3333182969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、準備出来たよ！\nこの衣装を着るとなんだか力がわいてきちゃうかも！",
      "startTime": 130.1666631698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、BIG4らしい風格が出てきていると思うぞ\nいいMVが撮れるといいな",
      "startTime": 139.066660118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.3333279608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "最後までしっかり見ててね\n月ストらしい、優しくてかっこいいMVにしちゃうから",
      "startTime": 143.7999934513,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11333.33988199999,
          "startTime": 155.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4333279608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そろそろ本番だね\nよーし、頑張ってくるね！",
      "startTime": 151.5999934513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.233323733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（どうやらリラックス出来ているようだ）\n（目標を考えることがいいきっかけになったのかもな）",
      "startTime": 160.333323733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.9999905585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃんみたいなアイドルを目指して頑張ってきた）\n（けど……BIG4になっても、気持ちは変わらないな）",
      "startTime": 168.9333339055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "（むしろ、昔より目標に近づいたから）\n（ずっとずっと強く思うようになったかも）",
      "startTime": 180.3333247502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃん……芽衣、これからも）\n（月ストのみんなと一緒に進んでいくよ）",
      "startTime": 190.2333196639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "（世界中の人がファンになってくれる）\n（そんな凄いアイドルになれるように）",
      "startTime": 197.2333166121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV公開から数日後",
      "startTime": 201.4000302312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 202.6666448592
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 202.6666448592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、MVの反応を見たか？\nSNSでも好評みたいだぞ",
      "startTime": 206.3666499454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_03-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　学校のお友達も褒めてくれたし\nファンのみんなも、感想を一杯投稿してくれてたよね！",
      "startTime": 212.0333166121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
